    "description": {
      "value": "\n                <i>Your spells have the maximum possible effect.</i>\n                <br />\n                <br />\n                \n                <p><b>Benefits</b></p>\n                <p><p class=\"stat-block-1\"> All variable, numeric effects of a spell modified by this feat are maximized. Saving throws and opposed rolls are not affected, nor are spells without random variables. A maximized spell uses up a spell slot three levels higher than the spell's actual level.</p><p class=\"stat-block-2\">An empowered, maximized spell gains the separate benefits of each feat: the maximum result plus half the normally rolled result.</p></p>\n                \n            \n            "
